Yesterday, the United Nations has proposed in Cancún a plan for the renewal of domestic, commercial and industrial lighting in hundreds of countries to reduce greenhouse gas (GEI) to an amount almost one-third of the additional reduction that needs to be carried out to stabilise the planet's climate by 2020.
